henteko vim settings

set:
$ git clone http://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/dotfiles_vim/vimfiles/vundle.git

$ ln -s ~/dotfiles_vim/_vimrc ~/.vimrc
$ ln -s ~/dotfiles_vim/vimfiles ~/.vim

vim -> :BundleInstall

$ make -f ~/dotfiles_vim/vimfiles/bundle/vimproc/make_mac.make

vim-latex setting for mac
$ sudo port -d selfupdate
$ sudo port -d sync

pTex install
$ sudo port install pTeX +hiragino +otf +utf8 +motif +macosx
